properties.remarks:
-Procedural Service available 
-ACFT OPR within or about to enter Indian Ocean UTA shall report position: 
a. Over UTA boundary 
b. Over any other point or time as instructed by ATC
All ACFT are suggested to keep contact Jakarta Radio HF on Frequency 11396 kHZ or 6556 kHZ or Logon CPDLC (WIIF)
